Invocation Name: breakfast sandwich
des:
Do you wake up hungry? Want to try a new idea for breakfast?
Breakfast Sandwich guides you through the ingredients and steps required to cook an egg and cheese sandwich. Use this skill in your kitchen to prepare a shopping list of ingredients, and later to perform all the steps required to cook an egg and cheese sandwich.

Say "next" as you follow each step. You can stop the skill part way through the recipe steps. When you relaunch the skill, it will ask you if you want to resume where you left off.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
